            <h2>What driveway drain cleaning actually solves</h2>
            <p>A driveway drain is the lowest point of the driveway and the first thing the water sees during a heavy rain. When leaves, sand, and mud fill the basin or the outlet line, the water has nowhere to go but into the garage or against the foundation.</p><p>Honest Drain pulls the grates, vacuums the basins, jets the outlet line, and confirms the drain ties into a working storm or daylight outlet.</p>
            <p class="link-row"><a class="text-link" href="../../../contact.html">Book a service visit</a></p>
